{"tid":915651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣丁守中提起選舉無效訴訟","createTime":"2018-11-25T06:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T08:47:29.000Z","uid":33890,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f597c26ee87fcc9ff902f850d9768b3b0f6f0ec3","tid":915651,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:49:12.000Z","msg":"中國國民黨台北市長候選人丁守中提起當選無效之訴，中選會副主委陳朝建今天說「尊重」，他強調，依照法律規定，下午4時前到投票所排隊的民眾仍可投票，以至於開票時間較晚。<br />\n台北市長選舉，開票逾10個小時才開出結果，台北市長柯文哲以58萬820票勝選連任，丁守中則以57萬7566票居次落選，兩人差距僅3254票。<br />\n丁守中質疑台北市一邊開票、一邊投票，過程中存在重大違法和太多疑點，決定提選舉無效訴訟並提出驗票要求。<br />\n開緊記者會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SVB1s7e-AVo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSVB1s7e-AVo&d=u3JrMCpuOh9JSbHLS7pmfv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ec22fa99\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SVB1s7e-AVo</a>"},{"pid":"796d79fed9319d6e241e1d4ed346af37153c1262","tid":915651,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21ed4d3d814383ee6910dc793e3c64245cae534","tid":915651,"uid":997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T07:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n姚弱智都唔敢出黎啦<br />\n選多次輸得仲慘"},{"pid":"ee45ba77c34f87c06a662f411e62626961d15216","tid":915651,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"796d79fed9319d6e241e1d4ed346af37153c1262","tid":915651,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,